<% content_for :body_class, 'with-cards vertical-center dark' %>
<div class="vertical-center">
	<div class="columns">
		<div class="landing-text column">
			<h1 class="header">Let's talk about risk</h1>

			<p>It's a fact: the only risk-free sex is no sex. But there are a limitless reasons to have sex, and limitless ways, and we think that's worthwhile. </p>

			<h2>Is risk limitless too?</h2>

			<p>The good news is, it's not. There are a lot of scare tactics and myths out there that can leave us confused about how much risk our sex lives really involve: Can we get or give an STI from that? When should we get tested? What will happen if a test comes back positive?</p>

			<h2>BedPost wants you to have the answers</h2>
			<p>Tailored to your body and the sex you have with it, BedPost helps you go confidently into the risky world of sex and handle what comes.</p>

			<p> And if you want to figure out how to reduce your risk? We've got tips for that too, but we're not pushy about it.</p>

		</div>
		<div class="login column">
			<div class="card">
				<div class="login">
					<h1>Sign up</h1>

					<%= vuelidate_form_with model: resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name), html: {class: "centered"}, require_all: true do |f| %>
						<%= f.text_field :name %>
						<%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email" %>
						<%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "new-password" %>
						<%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "new-password", show_toggle: true%>
						<%= f.submit "Sign up", id: "signup-submit", :class => "cta"%>
						<div class="additional">
							<%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>
	</div>
</div>
